{
  "texts": [
    "• In healthcare: In the healthcare field, chatbots suggest to patients related health information, diagnosis, and even therapy based on the received symptoms and data provided by the patient.",
    "They also offer the necessary information for the patient to receive the required service and product from the health provider for their care and needs.",
    "Chatbots became very popular in the healthcare sector during the COVID-19 pandemic, with all the restrictions and limitations imposed on physical contact with doctors and healthcare providers.",
    "However, it is worth mentioning that the healthcare sector is very cautious about using chatbots to deal with sensitive information that could negatively impact people's lives.",
    "They are not integrated to replace physicians' diagnoses completely but provide essential and first-help assistance to alleviate longer waiting time before interaction with the physician [14]."
  ]
}